# apple
IMAPAccount appleaccount
Host imap.mail.me.com
User thalesmg
PassCmd "pass imap.mail.me.com/mailpass"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs *
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore appleaccount-remote
Account appleaccount

MaildirStore appleaccount-local
Path ~/email/mbsyncmail/
Inbox ~/email/mbsyncmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel appleaccount
Far :appleaccount-remote:
Near :appleaccount-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge None
SyncState *
MaxMessages 100
ExpireUnread yes
